OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,8,FScott has been speaking to some
OL,9,Fresidents who are impacted by the
OL,10,Fmassive tip in Wigan.
OL,12,FA criminal investigation has begun
OL,13,Finto a massive 25,000 tonne fly-
OL,14,Ftipping site that has left some local
OL,15,Fresidents coping with infestations of
OL,16,Frats and flies.
