OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FDescribed as one of the largest in the
OL,8,Fcountry, the mountain of illegally fly-
OL,9,Ftipped waste, which is on a two acre
OL,10,Fsite in Wigan, sits next to houses, a
OL,11,Fplaying field and a primary school.
OL,13,FIt is believed the waste is partly on
OL,14,Fland owned by the Duchy of Lancaster,
OL,15,Fthe King's private estate, who say
OL,16,Fthey are working with Wigan Council
OL,17,Fand other agencies to sort the problem
OL,18,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
