OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FBut while there is some dispute about
OL,8,Fwho is responsible for cleaning it up,
OL,9,Fresidents living just metres away say
OL,10,Fthey cannot stand any more.
OL,12,FNisha Roson, who lives close by, said
OL,13,Fthe dump attracts seagulls, flies and
OL,14,Frats.
OL,16,FShe said: "The rats have gone
OL,17,Fcompletely out of control. We've had
OL,18,Frats in our cars, rats in our houses,
OL,19,Fwe see them wandering around on our
OL,20,Fstreet, they're just always about."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
