OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FThe rubbish tip sits on land on Bolton
OL,8,FHouse Road in Bickershaw, 30% of which
OL,9,Fis owned by the Duchy of Lancaster -
OL,10,Fprivate land of the King.
OL,12,FThe Duchy of Lancaster is exempt from
OL,13,Fregulations to clean the site due to
OL,14,Fan ancient legal framework from 750
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,FA spokesperson said that it does not
OL,18,Fhave to take responsibility for
OL,19,Fcleaning the land, instead offering it
OL,20,Fto Wigan Council to clean up.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
