OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Duchy of
OL,8,FLancaster said: "Approximately 30% of
OL,9,Fthe illegal tipping site vested to the
OL,10,FDuchy from its previous owner in July
OL,11,F2025 under a process known as escheat."
OL,13,F"At this point The Duchy contacted
OL,14,FWigan Council to seek a resolution,
OL,15,Fand we remain fully committed to
OL,16,Fworking with the local community and
OL,17,Frelevant agencies to address this
OL,18,Fissue and to counter the impact of
OL,19,Fillegal waste tipping."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
