OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FThe land was transferred to the King's
OL,8,Fprivate portfolio of estates in July
OL,9,F2025 in a process known as escheat as
OL,10,Fthe land is owned by a dissolved
OL,11,Fcompany.
OL,13,FFollowing the disclaimer of the
OL,14,Fdissolved company's ownership by the
OL,15,FTreasury Solicitor the land is in
OL,16,Feffect 'ownerless.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
