OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FThe Duchy of Lancaster collects assets
OL,8,Fof people who die without a will or
OL,9,Fnext of kin within the historic County
OL,10,FPalatine of Lancaster, as well as
OL,11,Fassets of dissolved companies, under
OL,12,Fthe ancient 'bona vacantia' legal
OL,13,Fprinciple.
OL,15,FThe illegal rubbish tip previously
OL,16,Fcaught fire in 2025, and burned for 10
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
