OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FA Wigan Council spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"The illegal waste site at Bolton
OL,9,FHouse Road has had, and continues to
OL,10,Fhave, a daily impact on residents who
OL,11,Flive nearby and on the bordering
OL,12,Fprimary school.
OL,14,F"The council believes that those who
OL,15,Fhave dumped the waste should be
OL,16,Fresponsible for its clean up, and
OL,17,Ffailing that the landowners. As one of
OL,18,Fthe impacted landowners, we are making
OL,19,Fefforts to clear the waste on our land.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
