OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,F"Local authorities also have an
OL,8,Fobligation to ensure best value for
OL,9,Fresidents. As such, the council would
OL,10,Fneed to consider the terms of any
OL,11,Farrangement the Duchy of Lancaster is
OL,12,Foffering since it is unlikely the
OL,13,Fvalue of the land would surpass the
OL,14,Fclean-up cost.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
