OL,3,C'The rats are out of control': The
OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,F"We continue to implore all landowners
OL,8,Fto take the necessary steps to fulfil
OL,9,Ftheir own obligations, and we call on
OL,10,Fthe government to make funding
OL,11,Favailable ` via the Environment Agency
OL,12,For other department ` to help remove
OL,13,Fthe waste, as has been done for other
OL,14,Fsites."
OL,16,FRubbish was first dumped on the site
OL,17,Fin October 2024, piling it up to 20
OL,18,Fmetres high, with the land already
OL,19,Fcovered in rubbish before ownership
OL,20,Fwas transferred to the Duchy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
