OL,4,Cmassive illegal waste dump on King's
OL,5,Cland
OL,7,FMakerfield MP Josh Simons told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "My constituents have been
OL,9,Fdealing with this for over a year now.
OL,11,F"It was last January that I started
OL,12,Fgetting reports from residents of
OL,13,Fwagons driving up the road dumping
OL,14,Fwaste, and ever since then, I've been
OL,15,Ftold and they've been told that
OL,16,Fagencies are working together in a
OL,17,Fgold team cross partnership way.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
